        "html": "<div class=\"wrap\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;min-height:90vh;background:var(--bg);overflow:hidden;\">\n\n  <!-- 좌측: 타이포그래피 임팩트 블록 -->\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:72px 48px 72px 64px;position:relative;\">\n\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2C2016 0%,#1E1610 100%);z-index:0;\"></div>\n\n    <div style=\"position:relative;z-index:1;\">\n      <span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.22em;color:var(--accent);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:24px;border:1px solid var(--accent);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:2px;\">7-Day Launch</span>\n\n      <h1 style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:clamp(42px,5.5vw,68px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.03em;color:#F5F0E8;margin:0 0 20px;\">\n        1주일,<br>\n        <span style=\"color:var(--accent);\">부캐</span>를<br>\n        세상에<br>\n        꺼낸다\n      </h1>\n\n      <div style=\"width:40px;height:3px;background:var(--accent);margin:24px 0;\"></div>\n\n      <p style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:clamp(14px,1.6vw,17px);line-height:1.75;color:#C4B8A8;max-width:340px;margin:0 0 40px;\">\n        Claude AI와 함께라면, 당신의 경험은\n        이미 팔 수 있는 서비스입니다.\n        7일 커리큘럼으로 지금 시작하세요.\n      </p>\n\n      <a href=\"#enroll\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:18px 40px;background:var(--accent);color:#1E1610;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.03em;border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;width:fit-content;\">지금 신청하기 <span style=\"font-size:20px;\">→</span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- 우측: 비주얼 + 포인트 리스트 -->\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:72px 48px;background:#141008;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n\n    <div style=\