span style=\"flex-shrink:0;width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:#1E1610;\">3</span>\n        <div><strong style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#F5F0E8;display:block;margin-bottom:2px;\">런칭 · 첫 고객 확보</strong>\n        <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:12px;color:#8A7C6E;\">6-7일차 · 오픈 전략 실행</span></div>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
